Wild Unknown Trial of Antiquity (c) Island Bar Games LLC

Release 06/10/2017

Protection: Steam
Game Size: 1 DISC

Game Type: Adventure, Indie [RELEASE NOTES]

Wild Unknown is a first-person adventure game where players
must explore, solve puzzles, and uncover hidden secrets in order
to piece together the surprising story of the mysterious
wilderness in which they awake

Trial of Antiquity features a completely new environment full of
brain-teasing puzzles and expands on the story of Wild Unknown
with some surprising revelations. The new content can be accessed
from the pause menu, or by finding one of the hidden endings in
the original game

The game is made standalone and includes all previous updates! [INSTALL NOTES] 1 Unpack 2 Mount / burn image 3 Install 4 Copy content from 'Crack' folder and replace game dir files 5 Play game 6 If U like it, buy it!
